fy_whoville_xmas Created by: Semp part of the FPSBANANA '08 Christmas contest Info: And he puzzled three hours, `till his puzzler was sore. This is a remake of COD's wetwork I started like five years ago. The initial project can be found here:

http://gamebanana.com/projects/34453

Technically, this is the remake of the remake since it is an adaptation of what the original remake was. This one features way better performance, more and better detail, lots of fixes of all kinds and a different theme which serves as an fps saver compared to the previous one.

The hull and the superstructure of the ship are made completely out of world brushes, so be grateful. It took many hours to build this.

Features:
LDR only lighting, tweaked and optimized nav file with place names, overview image, a few custom content, soundscapes, 64 player spawns, original COD's layout.

Recommended players: up to 28
Max recommended bots: up to 10


In case you want to review the project page of this version, here it is:
http://gamebanana.com/projects/34800  

Have fun!
Enjoy

Fy_weaver-smash has several secrets..

1:  Press the use button on any of the white orbs for various effect

2:  Try standing on the white orb that cries like an eagle..  follow the arrows up top.  Jump to get past the barrier at the     second arrow..
    If you have made it this far-  careful-  only half the top edge of the map has a no-clip rail..  meaning on half u CAN FALL OFF :D
    Jump onto the stone step to teleport..

3:  Shoot the third barrel on the other side of the water...

4:  The blue teleport in between the two sets of steps?  Yes, just have momentum you needn't take any damage.

5:  To the left of number 4's teleport, you can jump off the THIRD row of boxes, at jusssssssst the right spot, and teleport outside :)

--Weaver

THIS IS NOT THE SAME WATERWORLD THAT IS ON HERE.  I'VE HAD THE SAME NAME FOR MONTHS AND JUST REALIZED THERE WAS ANOTHER.

This is version 1.0 of my map, FY_Waterworld.  I'm not sure if there will be another version, but it helps to seperate from the other one I saw on here.  In fact I'm unsure if I put the right tag in front, but it's done and over with.

This map is a customized version of the Waterworld map from Resident Evil 4.  It's been modified to fit with the style of Counter-Strike with added cover, boxes, and ladders set around the map.  This is to hopefully detour SOME sniping, but I doubt that will keep people from pulling out the insta-kill guns.

Just want to note a couple things...
-Grates and windows are destructable
-There is no bot nav

I am by no means a master mapper since this was only my second map.  Please give any helpful tips or comments that may help improve things and do report any bugs that cause problems.  I'm hoping this will lead to making another map with renewed vigor.

*UPDATED IMAGES*
Also I looked at the map again after not looking at it for awhile and the texture glitches I thought were there are now gone.

IF YOU DOWNLOAD THIS MAP, PLEASE POST SOME FEEDBACK.  I'D LIKE TO KNOW HOW WELL IT RUNS WITH 10 TO 20 PEOPLE AND IF THERE ARE ANY MAJORS CHANGES THAT WILL BE NEEDED.

****THIS IS THE UPDATED VERSION OF THE ORIGINAL FY_WATERWORKS****

--------------------------------------------------------------

Fixed some fps problems by optimizing the map 
Fixed some minor bugs
Added some more detail to the map

Not any major changes with exception for the fps fix

I am aware that not everyone will get a constant 80 fps playing on this map, but detail come at a price. I asked my friend to test this on a really shitty computer, and he got a minimum of 35 fps :P
I guess thats what differs this from many other gg or fy maps out there. 

-------------------------------------------------------------

Hello everyone, and thanks for checking out my map! :D

This is the first map I am uploading, so if there's something you would like to me to know or change about the map, just post it in the comments.

I made this map because I am tired of playing gungame, fightyard and aim on maps that isn't very detailed or realistic. 
However, this map is, (imo :P) and have put alot of effort into making it so.

I couldn't really decide if this was a "fy", "aim" or "gg" map but I guess It can be used for any of them. 

I hope you will enjoy this map as much as me and my friends did!
Have fun and gimme lots of feedback!

---------------------------------------------------------------

Some features are 

64 player spawn 
Moving water that affects physics and players
3d skybox
Soundscapes

---------------------------------------------------------------

Install by extracting the bsp file to your counter-strike source/cstrike/maps
